Yii Framework
-------------
Fetch latest release of Yii Framework (required).

$ cd src
$ bash install.sh

Database
--------
Choose your favorite DB engine.

SQLite
------

$ cd src/protected/data
$ sqlite3 -init schema.sqlite.sql hamster.db
$ chmod 777 hamster.db

MySQL
-----

mysql> CREATE DATABASE hamster DEFAULT CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_general_ci;
$ cd src/protected/data
$ cat schema.mysql.sql | mysql -u root -p hamster

